5 E. For all new applicants not registered and in good standing
6 with the Construction Industries Board prior to July 1, 2026, the
7 Construction Industries Board will issue a residential roofer
8 endorsement to qualifying applicants no sooner than thirty (30) days
9 from the date of successful completion of the exam. New applicants
10 shall not be allowed to sell, offer, bid, inspect or perform any
